# Florine — environment variable template.
#
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in real values for local development.
# NEVER commit `.env` — it is gitignored. Real keys live ONLY in Vercel's
# dashboard (Project -> Settings -> Environment Variables), never in the repo.
#
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Tier 2 (AI-graded writing feedback) — NOT used in Phase 1.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Server-side only. Read by the /api/grade serverless function via
# process.env.GEMINI_API_KEY. The frontend never sees this value.
# Forkers must set their own key in their own Vercel deployment.
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-api-key-here
